Actress Idia Aisien has expressed irritation following a traumatic encounter. She’s particularly traumatised and irritated because she suffered humiliation from someone way below her status. She argued it’s delusional for anyone to treat another who is greater than them in a condescending manner. The TV presenter said: “I am honestly so traumatized and irritated by an encounter I had yesterday….. Humility isn’t by force but when you boast/talk down to anyone (particularly someone who has much more than you), it’s really unfortunate cause it borders on delusion.”   Portable exchanges ring with babymama on child’s christening     Tiwa becomes ambassador of popular smartphone brand     Worst experience with someone I dated – Nedu   Further expressing disgust, the media personality said the world would be a loveless sphere if everyone had to walk around exuding negative vibes. “If we all walked around with that negative energy, there’d be no love left in the world. Yuck!” she added.